qas.question: In May 2012, who started the parliamentary elections?
What led to the loss of power of traditional Greek parties?

answers.text: their support on the politics of Mnimonio and the austerity measures

qas.question: Who became the second major party after the elections?
What caused the second election of 2012?

answers.text: No party could form a sustainable government

qas.question: What was the demographic result of the second election?

answers.text: coalition government composed of New Democracy (29%), PASOK (12%) and Democratic Left (6%) parties.
